Booleans: true / false values using bool

Numbers: Unsigned (u8, u16, etc.) and signed (i32) integers, plus decimals (f32, f64)

Characters & Strings: Single characters with char, strings with &str and String

Arrays & Slices: Collections with fixed size, and partial views using slices ([start..end])

Tuples: Combine multiple types in one structured variable (("name", 25))

Mutability: All variables are immutable unless marked with mut
